expenses are $10,000.

00:00:10.910 --> 00:00:12.850
What is the minimum
number of computer

00:00:12.850 --> 00:00:15.410
she needs to sell in a
month to make a profit?

00:00:15.410 --> 00:00:17.975
So I'll let you think
about that for a second.

