Well, let's think about
what we have to figure out.

00:00:20.100 --> 00:00:21.766
We have to figure out
the minimum number

00:00:21.766 --> 00:00:23.240
of computers she needs to sell.

00:00:23.240 --> 00:00:25.770
So let's set that to a
variable or set a variable

00:00:25.770 --> 00:00:26.660
to represent that.

00:00:26.660 --> 00:00:30.770
So let's let x equal the
number of computers she sells.

00:00:30.770 --> 00:00:36.220
Number of computers sold.

00:00:36.220 --> 00:00:38.250
