And then, maybe she needs
to sell a little bit more

00:01:32.300 --> 00:01:33.880
than that.

00:01:33.880 --> 00:01:36.180
So let's see what gets
her to break even.

00:01:36.180 --> 00:01:38.150
So break even-- that's 0 profit.

00:01:38.150 --> 00:01:41.411
Neither positive or negative--
is equal to 27 times--

00:01:41.411 --> 00:01:42.910
and I'll do it all
in one color now.

